<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1002052">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1002052/" class="title-link">自己心中的《老子》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1002052"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/William/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1010305-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/William/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">William</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2005-08-05"
      class="main-meta">2005-08-05 14:22:12</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1002052_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读《老子》，最好先不要看白话注释，因为有时白话注释里有后人的曲解。众所周知的是，后代道教思想中搀杂有儒的思想，因此可能对理解老子真正的思想有误导。要形成自己心中的“道德”，这才是看本书最重要的意义所在。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1002052_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1002052_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
