  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4620093">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4620093/" class="title-link">正规蓝本</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4620093"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/heseri/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3007713-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/heseri/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">heseri</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-02-11"
      class="main-meta">2011-02-11 01:56:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4620093_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  河上公道德经章句，是道教界内部传习道德宝章的蓝本。内中很多见解和现在通行的白话版本不同，比如第一句，道可道非常道，河上公的断句是：道，可道，非常道。他认为道和可道是两种。自有一番道理。河上公章句尤其对修身，命功也有很大帮助。很多解释相当经典。所以力荐。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4620093/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4620093_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4620093_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





